{"tid":1573651,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登時報：華人可依靠抗暴鎮匪港人推翻政權","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T10:33:42.000Z","uid":284817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72f34213518d9911f2aed132d1854372b276a830","tid":1573651,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span>時報：<span style=\"color: red;\">華人</span>可依靠<span style=\"color: red;\">抗暴鎮匪港人推翻政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span>時報發表社評，指參加反修例示威的人<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span>了很多，證明港人<span style=\"color: red;\">真心認同</span>暴力，在<span style=\"color: red;\">外國</span>政府支持下，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港臨時政府及全世界華人</span>可以依靠<span style=\"color: red;\">抗暴鎮匪港人推翻政權</span>。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指出，香港作為自由港，非常容易受到<span style=\"color: red;\">中國等紅色國家</span>滲透，而且被揭發後並無後果；相反<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市民與外國</span>合作便被大做文章，證明現時<span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span>輿論非常激進。社評指，要維持香港社會的和諧，就必須將各階層、各群體的共同利益，變得超級強大，香港要有面向世界的包容，亦要有面向底層民眾的真正公平。<br />\n<br />\n文章又提到，大多數香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">非常願意攬炒</span>，就算<span style=\"color: red;\">持有外國護照的中國人</span>，都已經定居了香港很久，他們都希望維持香港繁榮穩定，移民<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大灣區</span></span>有很大風險及成本，而沒有外國護照的香港人，更有理由支持香港<span style=\"color: red;\">恢復自治</span>。</span>[/gold]"},{"pid":"d8147c8429c92586e34cc01b70ca42cb81c95023","tid":1573651,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"0cf44227f2eaedc6e4516b624926d0a2641b27d5","tid":1573651,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\